@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xbpcku(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(0.14)
    v1 = wp.abs((v1 / 0.80))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.54)))
    tmp = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.57 + v2 + 0.93) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.68)))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.87 * tmp + 0.71)) + ((v2 + 0.12 + v1 + 0.37) / v1))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.17 + tmp + 0.08)) / wp.cos((v0 + 0.36 - v2 + 0.62)))
    data[tid] = v0
